FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://cocktails.org/

# cocktailapp

Cocktail app is a simple API allowing to view cocktail recipies, and manage the ingredients.

## Recipes Collection [/recipes]

### List All Recipes [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 1,
                "name": "Negroni",
                "ingridients": [
                    {
                        "type": "Gin",
                        "units": "ml",
                        "amount": 30,
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "Campari",
                        "units": "ml",
                        "amount": 30,
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "Red Vermouth",
                        "units": "ml",
                        "amount": 30,
                    },
                ],
                "garnish": [
                    {
                        "type": "Orange Peel",
                        "units": "pcs",
                        "amount": "1"
