### Create a New Recipe [POST]

You may create your own cocktail recipe using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a recipe.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "Gin tonic",
            "ingridients": [
                {
                    "type": "Gin",
                    "units": "ml",
                    "amount": 50,
                },
                {
                    "type": "Tonic",
                    "units": "ml",
                    "amount": 100,
                }
            ],
            "garnish": [
                {
                    "type": "Orange Peel",
                    "units": "pcs",
                    "amount": "1"
                }
            ],
            "recipe": "Build with ice",
            "image": "gin_tonic.png",
            "glassType": "Rocks",
            "tags": ["IBA", "long"]
        }

